functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.

msg.content: In the last decade, in which year did the fewest California wildfires occur?
In the last decade, in which year did the fewest California wildfires occur?

The fewest number of California wildfires in the last decade occurred in 2011, with 7,985 wildfires. However, this was still a significant increase in wildfires compared to 2010, when there were 6,255 wildfires across the state.
